div1.p:
Office of the Sheriff of King County W. T. ss.
I, J. H. McGraw Sheriff of King County W. T. do hereby certify return to C. H. Hanford Chief Justice of Washington Territory that bfeore the coming to me of the within writ, the said William Jewett was committed to my custody, and is detained by virtue of another writ, a copy of which is hereto annexed the original of which I also herewith produce nevertheless I have the body of the said William Jewett before you at the time and place within mentioned as I am within commanded Dated at Seattle this 6th day of April 1889. J H McGraw Sheriff By DRM Kinlay Day Sheriffs Fees Serving Writ $1.00 Copies Com .80 Return 50 Travel 20 70 / $2.50
Filed April 5/89 W E Ledgerwood Clerk
